	</tbody>
</table>

<p>and here's what the completed stem-and-leaf plot would look like after a=
dding all 64 leaves to the nine stems:</p>

<p class=3D"text-align-center">&nbsp;</p>

<table class=3D"mx-auto" style=3D"width:100px;">
	<tbody>
